msgid ""
"Kollision is a casual game where you need to throw your ball and avoid the "
"others balls on the table as long as possible."
msgstr ""
"Kollision adalah permainan kasual di mana kamu harus melempar bola dan "
"menghindari lainnya yang mengamuk di atas meja selama mungkin."
